      <title>美联储官员柯林斯表示，美国通胀率将强劲攀升至 2% 目标</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-15/fed-s-collins-says-inflation-on-strong-trajectory-to-2-goal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[波士顿联邦储备银行行长苏珊·柯林斯表示，尽管数据可能每个月都有所波动，但她认为通胀率将回升至央行 2% 的目标。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-15/fed-s-collins-says-inflation-on-strong-trajectory-to-2-goal</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 15 Nov 2024 23:12:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
